or a pipe or
anything like that.

14:29.260 --> 14:31.399
No blood in the cab either.

14:31.430 --> 14:34.399
Looks like they just pulled him
out and executed him.

14:34.440 --> 14:36.533
Not a place I'd choose
to whack someone.

