on the side of the cab?

15:06.430 --> 15:07.260
You mean a face

15:07.300 --> 15:09.598
Yeah. Let's say Sajadi
is on his knees,

15:09.640 --> 15:11.301
hands behind his head.

15:11.340 --> 15:13.376
They shoot him,
it propels him forward,

15:13.410 --> 15:15.037
he hits his head on the cab.

15:15.080 --> 15:17.241
That could cause
the injuries, yeah.
If I'm right,

15:17.280 --> 15:18.508
the position he was in is part

15:18.550 --> 15:20.643
of an American military
detention protocol.

15:20.680 --> 15:22.648
Why would terrorists
waste time detaining him?

15:22.680 --> 15:25.342
