John".

34:23.860 --> 34:25.828
what you think you're seeing...

34:25.860 --> 34:28.829
it isn't real.

34:28.860 --> 34:30.828
What you remember,
it isn't true.

34:30.860 --> 34:33.499
How do you know?
You weren't there.

34:33.530 --> 34:36.761
But you were, and you can
remember the truth, can't you?

34:36.800 --> 34:38.768
Richie died.

34:38.810 --> 34:40.732
They blew him up.

34:40.770 --> 34:44.774
But what happened
before the explosion?

34:44.810 --> 34:46.346
Richie...

34:46.380 --> 34:47.779
RICHIE: I got this.
...broke cover.

34:47.810 --> 34:49.175
Richie, get back here!

34:49.220 --> 34:50.619
I told him no,
but still, he broke cover.

34:50.650 --> 34:51.787
Why?

34:51.820 --> 34:53.811
Why would he do that?

34:53.850 --> 34:55.181
I don't know!

34:55.220 --> 34:57.256
Yes, you do.
You can,

34:57.290 --> 34:58.689
you have to remember.

34:58.730 --> 35:00.357
Why?

35:00.390 --> 35:03.393
Because it's the only way
you're gonna learn the truth.

35:05.330 --> 35:07.298
It happened to me...

35:07.330 --> 35:09.264
John, the same thing.

35:09.300 --> 35:11.234
I...

35:11.270 --> 35:13.306
I lost someone a long time ago.

35:13.340 --> 35:14.807
And I thought
I remembered

35:14.840 --> 35:18.503
what happened to them,
and I was wrong.

35:21.820 --> 35:24.914
I want you to look at it.
Just look back, okay?

35:24.950 --> 35:27.282
It's like, um...
watching a movie.

35:27.320 --> 35:28.878
You know, you just...

35:28.920 --> 35:31.252
You look at the images
on the screen... you just...

35:31.290 --> 35:32.427
look at them.

35:32.460 --> 35:33.586
I'm afraid.

35:33.630 --> 35:34.927
You don't have
to be afraid.

35:34.960 --> 35:36.325
It's just a memory.

35:36.360 --> 35:38.260
It can't hurt you anymore.

35:38.930 --> 35:40.659
Richie left his cover.

35:40.700 --> 35:42.668
Why did he leave his cover?

35:45.210 --> 35:46.837
CURTIS:
Richie, get back!

35:46.870 --> 35:48.838
CURTIS:
Damn, I'm thirsty.

35:48.880 --> 35:49.778
You thirsty?

35:49.810 --> 35:50.777
About as thirsty as I was

35:50.810 --> 35:51.640
two minutes ago when you asked.

35:51.680 --> 35:55.218
Man, this blows.
Where did those guys go?

35:55.250 --> 35:56.672
Be here soon.

35:56.720 --> 35:58.688
It's like the inside
of my mouth is all stuck.

35:58.720 --> 36:00.187
Don't got any water on you?

36:00.220 --> 36:02.381
There's no
more water, bro.

36:02.420 --> 36:03.682
But that's fine.

36:03.720 --> 36:04.880
Let's just ride it out.

36:04.930 --> 36:06.921
We'll be fine.

36:10.560 --> 36:12.869
You see this?
We got a local.

36:17.500 --> 36:20.765
Damn it, they're
not stopping.

36:31.650 --> 36:33.618
The road was closed.

36:34.760 --> 36:37.456
Our orders were not
to let anyone pass.

36:37.490 --> 36:39.378
Road's closed! Get back!

36:40.760 --> 36:41.897
Get back!

36:47.270 --> 36:48.965
What the hell are they doing?

36:49.000 --> 36:50.490
I don't know.
I'm gonna go check it out.

36:50.540 --> 36:51.768
No, no, no. We have
orders to stay put.

36:51.810 --> 36:53.869
Only Richie didn't listen.

36:53.910 --> 36:55.730
Just be cool, bro.
It's just two guys, okay?

36:55.780 --> 36:57.475
Richie, don't!
I got this.

36:57.510 --> 36:59.341
Richie!

37:00.480 --> 37:02.573
Richie, get back here!

37:02.620 --> 37:03.848
Richie, I'm serious!

37:05.690 --> 37:07.715
Why did Richie leave his cover?

37:07.750 --> 37:08.648
What happened?
I don't know.

37:08.690 --> 37:10.988
I swear, I swear,
I don't... I don't know.

37:11.020 --> 37:13.250
But he-he put... he...

37:13.290 --> 37:14.826
He put some guy on the ground.

37:14.860 --> 37:16.919
Richie, get back here!
I'm serious!

37:16.960 --> 37:18.769
Richie?!

37:26.010 --> 37:27.534
RICHIE: Hands up
where I can see 'em.

37:31.750 --> 37:33.877
And that's when it blew up.

37:33.910 --> 37:35.844
It blew up after that.

37:35.880 --> 37:38.019
No, you're wrong.

37:38.050 --> 37:41.349
What happened after
he put the guy on the ground?

37:41.390 --> 37:43.449
I told you, I don't know!

37:43.490 --> 37:47.051
He went back to the car,
and he leaned in the window.

37:47.090 --> 37:48.398
No.

37:48.430 --> 37:49.590
Yes.

37:49.630 --> 37:51.029
Yes, and then he looked at you.

37:51.060 --> 37:53.767
No!

38:01.580 --> 38:04.970
Richie!

38:05.010 --> 38:06.705
What are you seeing?

38:06.750 --> 38:07.978
No.

38:31.140 --> 38:33.563
N0

38:35.540 --> 38:36.734
No.

38:36.780 --> 38:38.998
N0

38:39.050 --> 38:41.109
It was water.

38:41.150 --> 38:43.971
He got me water.

38:44.020 --> 38:45.339
I wanted water.

38:45.390 --> 38:46.982
He went and got me
some water.

38:47.020 --> 38:49.784
Hey, John, it's not your fault.

38:49.820 --> 38:52.129
None of this
is your fault, okay?

38:52.160 --> 38:53.957
I'm sorry.

38:53.990 --> 38:55.992
I'm so sorry.

38:56.030 --> 38:57.793
On your knees!
Get down on your knees!

38:57.830 --> 38:58.797
Don't move.
Hands behind your head.

38:58.830 --> 39:00.889
You're gonna be okay.
All right?

39:00.930 --> 39:02.659
You were brave enough

39:02.700 --> 39:03.962
to remember and find the truth.

39:04.000 --> 39:06.002
You're gonna be okay,
I promise you.

39:19.150 --> 39:20.117
You okay?

39:20.150 --> 39:22.482
Yeah, I'm fine.

39:22.520 --> 39:23.657
Interesting decision,

39:23.690 --> 39:26.488
going in against a guy with
a bomb and a gun, unarmed.

39:26.530 --> 39:29.658
A big...big gun.

39:29.700 --> 39:31.053
Yeah, so I heard.

39:31.100 --> 39:33.989
Probably should have
called or something, huh?

39:34.030 --> 39:35.998
Yeah. Or an e-mail.

39:36.040 --> 39:37.598
Thought you should know,

39:37.640 --> 39:40.063
I'm putting you up
for a blue bar, Medal of Valor.

39:40.110 --> 39:42.999
That-that is... not necessary.

39:43.040 --> 39:45.702
That decision is
above your pay grade, Detective.

39:45.750 --> 39:47.604
Okay.

39:47.650 --> 39:49.845
Well, it's good
for fund

39:49.880 --> 39:51.939
Look, I'm trying
to build something special here,

39:51.990 --> 39:53.844
something we can
all be proud of,

39:53.890 --> 39:56.484
and tonight,
I could not be more proud.

39:59.530 --> 40:01.794
Medal of valor, huh?
I saw the memo.

40:01.830 --> 40:03.024
It's impressive.

40:03.060 --> 40:04.925
Yes, but it wasn't
my idea.
Mm-hmm.

40:04.970 --> 40:06.961
It was Eliot's idea.

40:07.000 --> 40:09.662
You realize what you did was
way outside the rule book.

40:09.700 --> 40:11.065
Yeah, I do.

40:11.100 --> 40:12.067
I'm beginning to realize,

40:12.110 --> 40:14.578
you sort of got your
own rule book, don't you?

40:14.610 --> 40:15.804
I do.

40:19.050 --> 40:23.111
I asked my guy at the FBI
if he could pull some strings

40:23.150 --> 40:25.744
to get Mrs. Sajadi and her kids
their green cards.

40:25.790 --> 40:27.439
Well, I have a feeling

40:27.490 --> 40:29.219
that's way outside
the rule book.

40:29.260 --> 40:30.887
Yup.

40:36.160 --> 40:38.128
Hi.

40:38.160 --> 40:39.923
Hey.

40:44.540 --> 40:46.508
Did you hear about my blue bar?

40:46.540 --> 40:48.701
I heard a rumor about that.

40:48.740 --> 40:50.571
Congratulations.

40:50.610 --> 40:51.975
What happens to Curtis now, Al?

40:54.010 --> 40:55.841
Four combat tours.

40:55.880 --> 40:57.677
That's a lot to ask of anyone,

40:57.720 --> 40:59.210
much less a 24 year old.

41:01.120 --> 41:03.611
I guess where there's life,
there's hope, huh?

41:03.660 --> 41:06.584
He watched his best friend die.

41:06.630 --> 41:07.824
Mm.

41:07.860 --> 41:09.896
Sometimes our worst memories
have a way

41:09.930 --> 41:11.625
of making us forget
our best ones, right?

41:11.670 --> 41:13.922
That does not seem
like a fair trade, does it?

41:13.970 --> 41:16.530
Speaking of...

41:16.570 --> 41:18.606
June 5, 1999.

41:18.640 --> 41:20.608
Really?

41:20.640 --> 41:22.278
A Saturday night, as I recall.

41:22.310 --> 41:24.130
Just... you should just
let this one go.

41:24.180 --> 41:26.808
That Murphy bed was actually
prettycomfortable.
Yeah.

41:26.850 --> 41:29.216
It was really comfortable
until you flipped it up

41:29.250 --> 41:31.514
into the wall
with us inside of it.

41:31.550 --> 41:32.778
Ouch.

41:32.820 --> 41:34.139
That's not what you said
at the time.

41:34.190 --> 41:35.657
That is what I said.

41:35.690 --> 41:37.009
Are you actually
challenging my memory?

41:37.060 --> 41:38.186
I'm challenging your memory.

41:38.220 --> 41:39.551
I said, "Ouch," and then...?

41:39.590 --> 41:41.182
Distinctly recall...
I recall something, too.

41:41.230 --> 41:42.720
A kind of yell.

